                        <div class="category"><a href="/feature/">Feature</a>&nbsp;/&nbsp;<a href="/feature/art-culture/">Art & Culture</a></div>
                        <h1>Feast for eyes as works of over 150 artists to be displayed at Photofairs Shanghai</h1>
                        
                        <div class="app-visible">
                            <div class="authorList ">
                                
                                <div class="author  ">
                                    
                                    
                                    <div class="photoAuthor photoAuthor-inline photoAuthor-SHINE">
