<a href="/tanweiyun/" style="text-decoration: none;">
    <span class="photo" style="background:url(https://obj.shine.cn/files/author/30658f54-479c-447d-9b5c-ef0557fd51ae.jpg) no-repeat center center;background-size:cover;"></span>
