                                <div class="q"><div style="padding:1rem 0;">The ninth edition of Photofairs Shanghai, to be held at the Shanghai Exhibition Center from April 25 to 28, will include 46 exhibitors and the works of over 150 artists.</div></div>
                                <div style="clear:both;"></div>
